description:
Netbase, your semantic web database. 

Knowledge Graph containing over 600,000,000 nodes and statements, from all the Internet's finest sources, including Freebase, Wikidata, DBPedia, Yago, Wordnet, babelnet, ... as well as many custom GraphDBs.

From simple entities to complex queries, this is by far the fastest db of its kind.

Wikidata IDs work across the board and should become the new standard for common entities like places, celebrities etc!
